data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath lakefront home on cul-de sac in Waters Edge. One of the most sought after communities in Port Orange. As you approach this home you are welcomed by the gorgeous landscaping and "Pride of Ownership". Spacious open floor plan, split bedroom, vaulted ceilings and the parklike setting and lakeview from the living room and primary bedroom is breathtaking. Lot size is irregular and all information and measurements in MLS is deemed accurate but cannot be guaranteed and is to be verified by buyer and or buyers agent. ;Water: City
